Description. Body length up to 1.33 mm . Body light orange in alcohol (
Fig. 1
).

Antenna 1.8 of cephalic diagonal length. Antennal segments ratio as I: II: III: IV = 1 : 1.67–1.87 : 1. 27–1.53 : 2.67–2.93 . Smooth spiny mic at base of antennae 3 dorsal, 3 ventral on Ant. I, 1 internal, 1 external and 1 ventral on Ant. II. Ant. II distally with 1 sens having basal part expanded (
Fig. 11
). Two internal sens of Ant. III organ paddle-like; chaeta 8 dagger-like (
Fig. 12
